signatureAbility.signatureDescription: RAC receivers fight for every possible yard after making a catch. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on RAC catches against single coverage.
Ballcarriers with this ability have faster juke animations.
After securing a catch, ballcarriers with this ability can quickly shift momentum, change direction, and turn the corner without sacrificing speed.
The game's top defenders excel in all situations. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their chance of defeating run blocks, tackling runners, and disrupting catches.
Defenders with this ability don't allow broken tackles when hit-sticking ballcarriers - regardless of the runner's size or power.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
The game's top defenders excel in all situations. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their chance of defeating run blocks, tackling runners, and disrupting catches.
Defenders with this ability use faster run shed moves for a better chance at shedding blocks within 5 yards of the goal line.
